-----------------------------------------------------
-- This is a sample gnatcheck coding standard file --
-----------------------------------------------------
     
--  First, turning on rules, that are directly implemented in gnatcheck
   +RAbstract_Type_Declarations
   +RAnonymous_Arrays
   +REXIT_Statements_With_No_Loop_Name
   +RFloat_Equality_Checks
   +RGOTO_Statements
   +RImproper_Returns
   +ROTHERS_In_CASE_Statements
   +RUnconditional_Exits
   +RUnassigned_OUT_Parameters
   -- list of all rules: https://gcc.gnu.org/onlinedocs/gcc-4.5.4/gnat_ugn_unw/Predefined-Rules.html#Predefined-Rules
     
--  Then, also include ALL compiler checks:
   +RStyle_Checks:All_Checks

